{"tid":1767952,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[警報]五毛嘅目標喺大家嘅注意力","createTime":"2019-12-03T16:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T11:28:44.000Z","uid":74397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae7b84ff46b21c8e88d4db61c377e5a805f37d1","tid":1767952,"uid":74397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:32:11.000Z","msg":"由於五毛冇辦法del post<br />\n想令大家睇唔到行動post嘅方法就係洗板spin走啲有用資訊<br />\n我發現最近有啲account不斷share啲「新聞」<br />\n呢啲post有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>以下特點</strong></span>:<br />\n1. 冇內容出處，純copy and paste，唔似連登仔風格<br />\n2. 內容多數喺關於某啲人講咗啲咩 (包括中共，親共撚)<br />\n3. 標題誇張<br />\n4. 出post嘅人每日都會出大量post<br />\n<br />\n建議如下:<br />\n1. 見到五毛post，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好推</span></span>，唔好留言，最好完全唔理<br />\n2. 如果發現個account經常post呢啲嘢，最好就block咗佢<br />\n3. 每日都搵行動post嚟推，仲要得閒就推<br />\n<br />\n連登被嚴重滲透，呢個已經係常識<br />\n大家可能比較熟悉分化同放負呢兩招<br />\n最近仲有用啲刺激大家嘅內容嚟洗板，令到我地回覆推post，進而借力幫佢地洗板<br />\n當行動post out of insight嘅時侯，行動就容易out of mind<br />\n大家錯過咗行動，就等同與手足們割蓆<br />\n<br />\n希望手足們一齊幫幫手<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n以下係啲行動post:<br />\n12.8 港島遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767046\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767046</a><br />\n攬炒聖誕，正式啟動！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767451\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767451</a><br />\n[行動]12.8民陣 國際人權日遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1765090\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1765090</a>"},{"pid":"e0ff5c32732eca98082f739c9099046e5391114f","tid":1767952,"uid":74397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:32:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ce4d55bf7dd6325b76348277f3cf5f6b574436b5","tid":1767952,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff736196668e55439f2d505c7c4e31a4563ee016","tid":1767952,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:36:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},